    <div class="bg-radial-[at_90%_20%] md:bg-radial-[at_10%_50%] to-mongoose-950 from-mongoose-300">
        <Section>
            <Container>
                <h1 class="text-white">Dripping Springs Outdoor Powersport is your trusted, local repair facility.</h1>
            </Container>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-12 max-md:gap-y-16">
                <img src="https://imgix.cosmicjs.com/bdc03c70-d062-11f0-9412-e12f763e1300-side-view-man-repairing-motorcycle.jpg?w=1200" class="col-span-12 md:col-span-6 rounded-r-xl shadow-2xl h-full object-cover" />

                <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-6 lg:py-8 max-w-2xl">
                    <Container>
                        <div class="space-y-8">
                            <h2 class="heading-underline text-balance">Hey there, my name is Chris Porter.</h2>

                            <div class="text-mongoose-50 text-lg font-light space-y-6 tracking-normal">
                                <p>As the owner and operator of Flying Wrenches Mobile Powersports, my goal is simple: to make maintaining your powersports equipment as convenient as possible. I bring the shop to you!</p>
                                <p>As a factory-certified technician, I specialize in full-service repairs, custom installs, and routine maintenance for motorcycles, ATVs, utility vehicles, and dirt bikesâ€”all performed right at your door or ranch across Austin and the surrounding communities.</p>
                                <p>I'm committed to providing quality, professional repairs with the unmatched convenience you deserve, so you can spend less time moving your machine and more time riding it.</p>
                                <p>If you're ready to get started with Dripping Springs Outdoor Powersport, <a href="#" class="font-semibold underline">book an appointment</a>, and let's get started!</p>
                            </div>

                            <hr class="w-24 text-mongoose-400" />

                            <div class="flex gap-6 items-center">
                                <div class="button button-primary">Book Now!</div>
                                <div class="text-mongoose-100"><a href="#" class="font-semibold underline">See Our Services</a> &gt;</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </Container>
                </div>
            </div>
        </Section>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-mongoose-100">
        <Section>
            <Container>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-y-12 lg:gap-y-0 lg:gap-x-12 xl:gap-x-20">
                    <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-4 space-y-8">
                        <h2 class="heading-underline text-mongoose-950!">Our Services</h2>

                        <div class="space-y-6 mt-6 md:max-w-2xl">
                            <p class="text-mongoose-950">From routine manufacturer maintenance to complex engine rebuilds, Dripping Springs Outdoor Powersports is your trusted partner for reliability and performance.</p>
                            <p class="text-mongoose-950">We approach every repair with meticulous attention to detail and factory-level diagnostic precision, ensuring your ATV, UTV, or outdoor equipment is fixed right the first time and ready to handle the toughest Hill Country terrain.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-8 space-y-24">
                        {[...Array(3)].map((_, index) => <Service />)}
                    </div>
                </div>
            </Container>
        </Section>
    </div>

